abx^2 = (a-b)^2(x+1)
\sqrt{1+{4\over x}+{4\over x^2} }
a+b \over a-b
a-b\over a+b
a^2+ab
\textbf{Shortest Solution}
\frac{ab}{(a-b)^2}=\frac{(x+1)}{x^2}
\frac{ab}{(a-b)^2}=\frac{1}{x^2}+\frac{1}{x}
4
\frac{4ab}{(a-b)^2}=\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}
1
1+\frac{4ab}{(a-b)^2}=1+\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}
\frac{(a-b)^2+4ab}{(a-b)^2}=1+\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}
\frac{(a+b)^2}{(a-b)^2}=1+\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}
\sqrt{\frac{(a+b)^2}{(a-b)^2}}=\sqrt{1+\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}}
\frac{(a+b)}{(a-b)}=\sqrt{1+\frac{4}{x^2}+\frac{4}{x}}
({1+\frac{2}{x}})^2
1+\frac{2}{x}
x=\frac{-b+\sqrt{b^2-4ac}}{2a}
\frac{a+b}{a-b}
x
abx^2-(a-b)^2x-(a-b)^2=0
x=\frac{(a-b)^2 \pm \sqrt{(a-b)^4+4ab(a-b)^2}}{2ab}
x=\frac{(a-b)^2\pm \sqrt{a^4+b^4-4a^3b-4ab^3+6a^2b^2+4a^3b+4ab^3-8a^2b^2}}{2ab}
(a-b)^4
x=\frac{2a^2-2ab}{2ab}
\sqrt{1+\frac{4}{x}+\frac{4}{x^2}}=\sqrt{\bigg(1+\frac{2}{x}\bigg)^2}
1+\frac{2}{x}=1+\bigg(\frac{4ab}{2a^2-2ab}\bigg)=\frac{a+b}{a-b}
\sqrt{1+\frac{4}{x}+\frac{4}{x^2}}=\sqrt{\frac{1}{x^2}(x+2)^2}
